article_id:1178,category_name:News,title_name:Limited-Time Packs Are Here!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/9c6399170214a1bdd2084f44dba4cd6a.png,message:<div>Limited-time packs are available under Limited-Time Deals in the Shop as of <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585288800"></span>!</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/9c6399170214a1bdd2084f44dba4cd6a.png"></div><div><br></div><div>■Availability Period</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585288800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1586757540"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Check out the details for each pack below.</div><div><br></div><div>■Limited-Time Sunlight Stone Quad-Pack</div><div>This pack contains diamantium and items useful for upgrading dragons.</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Diamantium Included&gt;</div><div>・Diamantium x4,800 (3,920 + 880 bonus)</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Other Items Included&gt;</div><div>・Sunlight Stone x4</div><div><br></div><div>■Limited-Time Diamantium Mega-Pack</div><div>This pack contains a large amount of diamantium.</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Diamantium Included&gt;</div><div>・Diamantium x5,700 (3,920 + 1,780 bonus)</div><div>Note:</div><div>・This product is not available in some countries/regions.</div><div><br></div><div>■Limited-Time 5★ Dragon Upgrade Special</div><div>This pack contains diamantium, a voucher to summon a 5★ dragon, and items useful for upgrading dragons.</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Diamantium Included&gt;</div><div>・Diamantium x2,400 (1,920 + 480 bonus)</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Other Items Included&gt;</div><div>・5★ Summon Voucher (Dragon) x1</div><div>・Sunlight Stone x1</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>・When you have a 5★ Summon Voucher (Dragon), you can perform a 5★ Dragon Summon from the main Summon page.</div><div>・In a 5★ Dragon Summon, you use a 5★ Summon Voucher (Dragon) and will be guaranteed to summon one 5★ dragon.</div><div>・To check appearance rates for the 5★ Dragon Summon, open the Shop from the Home page, then select Limited-Time Deals, pick the Limited-Time 5★ Dragon Upgrade Special, and select 5★ Dragon Appearance Rates in the pop-up that appears after tapping Purchase.</div><div>・This product is not available in some countries/regions.</div><div><br></div><div>■Limited-Time 5★ Dragon Pack</div><div>This pack contains diamantium and a voucher to summon a 5★ dragon.</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Diamantium Included&gt;</div><div>・Diamantium x1,500 (1,200 + 300 bonus)</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Other Items Included&gt;</div><div>・5★ Summon Voucher (Dragon) x1</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>・When you have a 5★ Summon Voucher (Dragon), you can perform a 5★ Dragon Summon from the main Summon page.</div><div>・In a 5★ Dragon Summon, you use a 5★ Summon Voucher (Dragon) and will be guaranteed to summon one 5★ dragon.</div><div>・To check appearance rates for the 5★ Dragon Summon, open the Shop from the Home page, then select Limited-Time Deals, pick the Limited-Time 5★ Dragon Pack, and select 5★ Dragon Appearance Rates in the pop-up that appears after tapping Purchase.</div><div>・This product is not available in some countries/regions.</div><div><br></div><div>■Limited-Time Superior Orb Pack</div><div>This pack contains diamantium and items useful for unlocking mana nodes.</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Diamantium Included&gt;</div><div>・Diamantium x1,500 (1,200 + 300 bonus)</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Other Items Included&gt;</div><div>・Incandescence Orb x50</div><div>・Tsunami Orb x50</div><div>・Tempest Orb x50</div><div>・Resplendence Orb x50</div><div>・Abaddon Orb x50</div><div>・Champion&#39;s Testament x4</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. See Appearance Rates on the pack purchase screen for information about the lineup of dragons available using the 5★ Summon Voucher (Dragon).</div><div>2. For information about each pack, select the Shop on the Home page, and see Limited-Time Deals.</div><div>3. The Limited-Time Diamantium Mega-Pack may be purchased up to three times during the availability period. Other limited-time packs may only be purchased once during the availability period.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1585288800,update_time1585401462